snippet.title: Race Highlights | 2025 Australian Grand Prix
snippet.description:

nl.description: Herbeleef de ongelooflijke actie van de Grand Prix van Australië, met meerdere crashes, wisselende weersomstandigheden, Safety Cars en een late regenbui die tot aan de laatste vlag voor drama zorgde.

es.title: Mejores Momentos | Gran Premio de Australia 2025
es.description: Revive toda la acción del Gran Premio de Australia donde se han visto: múltiples accidentes, condiciones climáticas cambiantes, coches de seguridad y un chaparrón al final que ha generado momentos dramáticos hasta la bandera de cuadros.

fr.title: Meilleurs Moments | Grand Prix d'Australie 2025
fr.description: Revivez le meilleur d'un incroyable Grand Prix d'Australie, avec de nombreux crash, des conditions changeantes, des voitures de sécurité et une averse en fin de course garantissant des rebondissements jusqu'au drapeaux à damier.

snippet.title: Can You Fool A Self Driving Car?
snippet.description:
Never underestimate the power of freakin' lasers! Have fun learning to think like an engineer and get 2 FREE boxes at: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

Get your CrunchLabs box today:
Build Box for kids click here: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
Hack Pack for teens and adults click here: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

Full un-cut footage from the fake wall crash: https://x.com/MarkRober/status/1901449395327094898 s=46

Thanks to Luminar for allowing us to test their LiDAR-equipped car. They provided the vehicle for testing purposes, but no compensation was given, and this is not a paid promotion: https://www.luminartech.com/

pa.title: ਕੀ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਇੱਕ ਸਵੈ-ਚਲਾਉਣ ਵਾਲੀ ਕਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਠੱਗ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ?

ਲੇਜ਼ਰਾਂ ਦੀ ਤਾਕਤ ਨੂੰ ਕਦੇ ਘਟਾ ਨਾ ਅੰਕਣਾ! ਇਕ ਇੰਜੀਨੀਅਰ ਵਾਂਗ ਸੋਚਣਾ ਸਿੱਖਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਮਜ਼ਾ ਆਉ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar 'ਤੇ 2 ਮੁਫਤ ਬਾਕਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਆਪਣਾ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਬਾਕਸ ਅੱਜ ਹੀ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ:
ਬੱਚਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਬਿਲਡ ਬਾਕਸ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
ਟੀਨ ਏਜਰ ਅਤੇ ਵੱਡਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਹੈਕ ਪੈਕ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

ਸਾਡੇ ਨਾਲ ਆਪਣੀ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਕਾਰ ਟੈਸਟ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਲੂਮਿਨਾਰ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ: https://www.luminartech.com/

ਰਾਕ ਰੋਬੋਟਿਕ ਦੇ ਹੈਰਿਸਨ @IndianaDrones ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ ਜੋ ਆਪਣੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਕੂਲ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਨਾਲ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਮਿਲੇ। ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰਜੈਕਟ ਤੋਂ ਸਕੈਨਸ ਅਤੇ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਦਾ 3D ਟੂਰ ਦੇਖਣ ਲਈ ਤੁਸੀਂ https://www.rockrobotic.com/ 'ਤੇ ਜਾ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ।

നിങ്ങളുടെ കുഞ്ഞുങ്ങളായും യുവാക്കളായും അഡൾട്ട്സായും ക്രഞ്ച്‌ലാബ്സ് ബോക്സ് ഇന്ന് ലഭ്യമാക്കൂ:
കുട്ടികൾക്കായുള്ള ബിൽഡ് ബോക്സ് ഇവിടെ ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്യുക: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

ലുമിനാറിനെ നന്ദി, അവരുടെ ലിഡാർ കാർ പരീക്ഷിക്കാൻ അനുവദിച്ചതിന്: https://www.luminartech.com/

റോക്ക് റോബോട്ടിക്യിലെ ഹാരിസൺ @IndianaDrones യുടെ വളരെ ത്രസിപ്പിക്കുന്ന ലിഡാറിനൊപ്പം സഹകരിക്കാന് നന്ദി. നിങ്ങളുടെ പ്രോജക്ടിന്റെ സ്കാൻഗലകളും ക്രഞ്ച്‌ലാബ്സിന്റെ 3ഡി ടൂറും സന്ദർശിക്കാൻ https://www.rockrobotic.com/ സന്ദർശിച്ചുകൊണ്ട്.

snippet.title: Chaotic 4x400 caps men's 2025 NCAA indoor championship
snippet.description:
Watch all three sections of the men's 4x400m final — and the lengthy delay/review that followed — at the 2025 NCAA indoor track and field championships. Southern California won the 2025 Division I men's indoor track and field title, clinching the title with the meets final event — the chaotic 4x400 meter relay. Texas A&M got disqualified for flagrantly impeding Arkansas, which campaigned for a re-run of the race but was denied.

After the dust settled, USC outpaced Arkansas to score five points in the 4x4 to give the Trojans the championship win by six points. In total, USC finished with 39 points, while Georgia finished with 33 points in second place. It's USC's first men's indoor title in 53 years.

Subscribe to the NCAA Championship YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/NCAAChampionships?sub_confirmation=1

Get your NCAA Championship tickets here: https://www.ncaatickets.com/

en.title: Chaotic 4x400 caps men's 2025 NCAA indoor championship
en.description:
Watch all three sections of the men's 4x400m final — and the lengthy delay/review that followed — at the 2025 NCAA indoor track and field championships. Southern California won the 2025 Division I men's indoor track and field title, clinching the title with the meets final event — the chaotic 4x400 meter relay. Texas A&M got disqualified for flagrantly impeding Arkansas, which campaigned for a re-run of the race but was denied.

After the dust settled, USC outpaced Arkansas to score five points in the 4x4 to give the Trojans the championship win by six points. In total, USC finished with 39 points, while Georgia finished with 33 points in second place. It's USC's first men's indoor title in 53 years.

Subscribe to the NCAA Championship YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/NCAAChampionships?sub_confirmation=1

snippet.title: Kingdom Come Deliverance 2 IS A PERFECTLY BALANCED GAME WITH NO EXPLOITS
snippet.description:
KCD2 Is here and it is rapidly becoming one of the greatest RPGs of all time! Of course as a fan of open world sandbox rpgs like skyrim I am drawn to the adventure that kingdom come deliverance has to offer. Of course similar to your average elder scrolls game the developers have left in some perfectly balanced game design choices that might result in the spiffing brit having to ask an important question. Is Kingdom Come Deliverance 2 A Perfectly balanced game with no exploits? Or perhaps are there bugs, glitches and overpowered features that spiff can use to turn himself into a god. 

What you have seen here today is part of a fantastic perfectly balanced gameplay series on youtube where I go from game to game and break them with wacky exploits to gain things like unlimited gold and infinite money all in a fantastic montage. If you enjoyed this then be sure to check out more. The style is similar to RT game and callmekevin in parts. A large influence on this series has come from Valefisk and The Killian Experience. 

Chapters:
00:00 Hello Henry 
00:32 Green Thumb
02:58 Let Him Cook
04:22 He can go all night
07:03 Gimblong
09:23 Stop! That’s Illegal
12:57 Is this Groundhog Day?
14:12 With Great Dice Comes Great..
12:50 With Great Money Comes Great..
18:56 They Call him Heizenbard
20:28 The most Overpowered Ability
22:25 A Final Quest
23:44 A Final Side Adventure
25:13 Monk Mode

snippet.title: Finally! US is Testing Brand New B-52s To Fly For A Full Century!
snippet.description:
When the B-52 Stratofortress made its first flight in 1952, no one could have imagined that this bomber would survive not only the Cold War, but the turn of the century, as well!
Today, more than 70 years later, it not only remains in service, but is also undergoing another modernization that can ensure its combat effectiveness for several more decades!
Now let’s take a look at how an ordinary turboprop project from the mid-20th century became a symbol of the strategic power of the 21st century!

To see what I do behind the scenes or outside my videos, follow me on Instagram

📸 Personal Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tylerhartlauer/
📱Tik Tok: tiktok.com/@td_the_creator
✉️ Email for business reasons: td.brickz@gmail.com

Credits:
Non copyright music from Epidemic Sound: https://share.epidemicsound.com/c3oiyn
Outro song from NBHD Nick: https://linktr.ee/nbhdnick 
Background beats from Bakkstab: https://soundcloud.com/realbakkstab
Background beats: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=43MQ4Bfhrlw
Lil Tecca inspired AI song by Torns: https://open.spotify.com/artist/2xnJVU1K87J1Mxi95MWqgK?si=tECJ002rQDO92AmW10w8fg
Netflix inspired outro by Kevin Guinn
Background beats by @xRyBeatzCEOx 
Outro by @Keshen8 

Frequently asked questions:
Where do I get my Lego?
- Bricklink.com, Lego Store
How do I make my videos?
- To edit, I use Final Cut Pro X. To film, I use a Canon EOS R8 and my iPhone. To record my voice, I use a RODE VideoMic Go.
Do I have instructions for my Lego builds?
- I sadly don’t
What do I do with my Lego builds after a video is finished?
- I usually have to take them apart to use for the next Lego build I make

snippet.title: Blastoff! NASA's SpaceX Crew-10 launches to space station, booster lands in Florida
snippet.description:
A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket launched the Crew-10 mission for NASA from Launch Complex-39 at the Kennedy Space Center (KSC) in Florida on March 14, 2025 at 7:03 p.m. EST (2348 GMT). Full Story: https://www.space.com/space-exploration/international-space-station/spacex-launches-relief-crew-for-nasas-beleaguered-starliner-astronauts-on-iss-video

Crew-10 is NASA astronauts Anne McClain and Nichole Ayers, JAXA (Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency) astronaut Takuya Onishi and Roscosmos cosmonaut Kirill Peskov. 

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: An Exquisitely Unusual Tiny Home Built With Nature’s Geometry
snippet.description:
This is a tiny house that immediately captured my heart. There's something about the curved roof, the stained glass windows and the rounded doors that remind me of a modern hobbit-like home that just radiates warmth, character and comfort. 

Philippa is a remarkable woman. I enjoyed my time with her immensely. I can always tell when I meet a kindred spirit and I felt this way with her. You know that when you meet a person who can talk with penguins, you've met someone very special indeed. She has lived a big life and done some remarkable things, One of those things is building her tiny house. A very bespoke home that sings to her soul. 

And this home! Beautiful and character filled. It's enough, and yet it's so much more. From the beautiful shapes and all the wonderful adornments this is a house that radiates a very real sensation of home. 

Nature has very few right angles, and that trait is shared with this tiny home. A true labour of love for Philippa and her builders, this is a tiny house not to be forgotten. Crafted with sacred geometric principles in mind, this could very easily be your new favourite tiny home. We very much hope you enjoy the tour. 

You can find out more about Philippa, her writing and links to listen to her podcast via her website: https://philippaross.com

If you enjoy our show and would like to help support our work, please consider supporting us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/livingbig

Our Socials and Links: https://linktr.ee/livingbig

Find out more about this tiny house and others on our website: https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/

Please subscribe for more videos on tiny houses, architecture, DIY, design, and sustainable, off-grid living.

Presented and Produced by: Bryce Langston
Camera: Rasa Pescud & Bryce Langston
Editing:  Sarah Binder & Rasa Pescud

pt-BR.title: Uma casa minúscula e requintadamente incomum construída com a geometria da natureza
pt-BR.description:
Esta é uma casa minúscula que imediatamente conquistou meu coração. Há algo no telhado curvo, nos vitrais e nas portas arredondadas que me lembram de uma casa moderna estilo hobbit que simplesmente irradia calor, caráter e conforto. 

Philippa é uma mulher extraordinária. Gostei muito do meu tempo com ela. Sempre sei quando encontro uma alma gêmea e me senti assim com ela. Você sabe que quando conhece uma pessoa que consegue falar com pinguins, você conheceu alguém muito especial. Ela viveu uma vida grande e fez coisas extraordinárias. Uma dessas coisas é construir sua casa minúscula. Uma casa muito personalizada que canta para sua alma. 

E esta casa! Linda e cheia de caráter. É o suficiente, e ainda assim é muito mais. Das belas formas e todos os adornos maravilhosos, esta é uma casa que irradia uma sensação muito real de lar. 

A natureza tem poucos ângulos retos, e essa característica é compartilhada com esta casa minúscula. Um verdadeiro trabalho de amor para Philippa e seus construtores, esta é uma pequena casa para não ser esquecida. Criada com princípios geométricos sagrados em mente, esta pode facilmente ser sua nova pequena casa favorita. Esperamos muito que você aproveite o passeio. 

Você pode descobrir mais sobre Philippa, seus escritos e links para ouvir seu podcast através de seu site: https://philippaross.com

de-DE.title: Ein äußerst ungewöhnliches kleines Haus, gebaut nach der Geometrie der Natur
de-DE.description:
Dieses Tiny House hat mich sofort in seinen Bann gezogen. Das geschwungene Dach, die Buntglasfenster und die runden Türen erinnern mich an ein modernes Hobbit-Haus, das Wärme, Charakter und Behaglichkeit ausstrahlt.

Philippa ist eine bemerkenswerte Frau. Ich habe die Zeit mit ihr sehr genossen. Ich spüre immer, wenn ich eine Seelenverwandte treffe, und so ging es mir auch mit ihr. Wer jemanden trifft, der mit Pinguinen sprechen kann, hat etwas ganz Besonderes gefunden. Sie hat ein erfülltes Leben geführt und Bemerkenswertes geleistet. Dazu gehört auch der Bau ihres Tiny House. Ein maßgeschneidertes Zuhause, das ihre Seele berührt.

Und dieses Haus! Wunderschön und voller Charakter. Es ist genug und doch so viel mehr. Die schönen Formen und die vielen wundervollen Verzierungen vermitteln ein Gefühl von Zuhause.

In der Natur gibt es nur wenige rechte Winkel, und genau das trifft auch auf dieses Tiny House zu. Dieses Tiny House ist ein wahres Herzensprojekt von Philippa und ihren Erbauern – ein unvergessliches Erlebnis. Dieses nach den Prinzipien der heiligen Geometrie gestaltete Tiny House könnte Ihr neues Lieblings-Tiny House werden. Wir hoffen, Ihnen gefällt die Tour.

it.title: Una minuscola casa squisitamente insolita costruita con la geometria della natura
it.description:
Questa è una casa minuscola che mi ha subito conquistato il cuore. C'è qualcosa nel tetto curvo, nelle vetrate colorate e nelle porte arrotondate che mi ricorda una moderna casa in stile hobbit che irradia calore, carattere e comfort. 

Philippa è una donna straordinaria. Mi sono divertito moltissimo con lei. Riesco sempre a capire quando incontro un'anima gemella e mi sono sentito così con lei. Sai che quando incontri una persona che sa parlare con i pinguini, hai incontrato qualcuno di molto speciale. Ha vissuto una grande vita e ha fatto cose straordinarie, una di queste è stata costruire la sua casa minuscola. Una casa molto su misura che canta alla sua anima. 

E questa casa! Bella e piena di carattere. È abbastanza, eppure è molto di più. Dalle belle forme e da tutti i meravigliosi ornamenti questa è una casa che irradia una sensazione molto reale di casa. 

La natura ha pochissimi angoli retti e questa caratteristica è condivisa con questa casa minuscola. Un vero lavoro d'amore per Philippa e i suoi costruttori, questa è una casa minuscola da non dimenticare. Realizzata con principi geometrici sacri in mente, questa potrebbe facilmente diventare la tua nuova casa minuscola preferita. Ci auguriamo vivamente che ti piaccia il tour. 

Puoi scoprire di più su Philippa, i suoi scritti e i link per ascoltare il suo podcast tramite il suo sito web: https://philippaross.com

Se ti piace il nostro spettacolo e vuoi aiutare a sostenere il nostro lavoro, ti preghiamo di considerare di supportarci su Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/livingbig

es-US.title: Una pequeña casa exquisitamente inusual construida con la geometría de la naturaleza
es-US.description:
Esta minicasa me cautivó al instante. El techo curvo, las vidrieras y las puertas redondeadas tienen algo que me recuerda a una casa moderna estilo hobbit, que irradia calidez, carácter y comodidad.

Philippa es una mujer extraordinaria. Disfruté muchísimo de mi tiempo con ella. Siempre sé cuándo conozco a alguien afín, y me sentí así con ella. Sabes que cuando conoces a alguien que puede hablar con pingüinos, conoces a alguien muy especial. Ha vivido una vida plena y ha hecho cosas extraordinarias. Una de ellas es construir su minicasa. Una casa hecha a medida que le llega al alma.

¡Y esta casa! Hermosa y llena de carácter. Es suficiente, pero a la vez es mucho más. Desde las hermosas formas hasta los maravillosos adornos, esta casa irradia una auténtica sensación de hogar.

La naturaleza tiene muy pocos ángulos rectos, y esta minicasa comparte esa característica. Un verdadero trabajo de amor por parte de Philippa y sus constructores, esta minicasa es inolvidable. Diseñada con principios de geometría sagrada, podría convertirse fácilmente en tu nueva minicasa favorita. Esperamos que disfrutes del recorrido.

id.title: Rumah Mungil yang Luar Biasa dan Unik yang Dibangun dengan Geometri Alam
id.description:
Ini adalah rumah mungil yang langsung menarik hati saya. Ada sesuatu tentang atap melengkung, jendela kaca patri, dan pintu bundar yang mengingatkan saya pada rumah modern mirip hobbit yang memancarkan kehangatan, karakter, dan kenyamanan. 

Philippa adalah wanita yang luar biasa. Saya sangat menikmati waktu saya bersamanya. Saya selalu tahu ketika saya bertemu dengan jiwa yang sama dan saya merasakan hal ini bersamanya. Anda tahu bahwa ketika Anda bertemu seseorang yang dapat berbicara dengan penguin, Anda telah bertemu seseorang yang sangat istimewa. Dia telah menjalani kehidupan yang hebat dan melakukan beberapa hal yang luar biasa. Salah satunya adalah membangun rumah mungilnya. Rumah yang sangat dipesan khusus yang bernyanyi bagi jiwanya. 

Dan rumah ini! Indah dan penuh karakter. Itu cukup, namun masih jauh lebih dari itu. Dari bentuknya yang indah dan semua hiasan yang indah, ini adalah rumah yang memancarkan sensasi rumah yang sangat nyata. 

Alam memiliki sangat sedikit sudut siku-siku, dan sifat itu juga dimiliki oleh rumah mungil ini. Sebuah karya cinta sejati bagi Philippa dan para pembangunnya, ini adalah rumah mungil yang tak terlupakan. Dibuat dengan prinsip-prinsip geometri suci, ini bisa dengan mudah menjadi rumah mungil favorit baru Anda. Kami sangat berharap Anda menikmati tur ini.

Anda dapat mengetahui lebih lanjut tentang Philippa, tulisannya, dan tautan untuk mendengarkan podcastnya melalui situs webnya: https://philippaross.com

ja.title: 自然の幾何学的形状で建てられた、非常に珍しい小さな家
ja.description:
これはすぐに私の心をとらえた小さな家です。曲線の屋根、ステンドグラスの窓、丸いドアには、暖かさ、個性、快適さを放つモダンなホビットのような家を思い起こさせる何かがあります。

フィリッパは素晴らしい女性です。彼女と一緒に過ごした時間はとても楽しかったです。私はいつも、気の合う人に出会ったと感じます。そして、彼女といるとそう感じました。ペンギンと話せる人に出会ったら、本当に特別な人に出会ったということです。彼女は素晴らしい人生を送り、いくつかの素晴らしいことを成し遂げました。その一つが、小さな家を建てたことです。彼女の魂に響く、とても特注の家です。

そして、この家！美しく、個性にあふれています。それだけで十分ですが、それだけではありません。美しい形とすべての素晴らしい装飾から、この家はまさに本当の我が家の感覚を放っています。

自然には直角がほとんどなく、その特徴はこの小さな家にも共通しています。フィリッパと彼女の建築者たちの真の愛情の結晶であるこの小さな家は、忘れられないものです。神聖幾何学の原理を念頭に置いて作られたこの家は、あなたの新しいお気に入りの小さな家になることは間違いありません。ツアーを楽しんでいただければ幸いです。

フィリッパについて、彼女の執筆活動、ポッドキャストを聴くためのリンクについては、彼女のウェブサイトで詳しく知ることができます: https://philippaross.com

hi.title: प्रकृति की ज्यामिति से निर्मित एक अत्यंत असामान्य छोटा सा घर
hi.description:
यह एक छोटा सा घर है जिसने तुरंत मेरा दिल जीत लिया। घुमावदार छत, रंगीन कांच की खिड़कियां और गोल दरवाज़ों में कुछ ऐसा है जो मुझे एक आधुनिक हॉबिट-जैसे घर की याद दिलाता है जो गर्मजोशी, चरित्र और आराम को बिखेरता है।

फिलिपा एक असाधारण महिला हैं। मैंने उनके साथ अपना समय बहुत एन्जॉय किया। मैं हमेशा बता सकता हूं कि मैं कब किसी आत्मीय आत्मा से मिलता हूं और मैंने उनके साथ ऐसा ही महसूस किया। आप जानते हैं कि जब आप किसी ऐसे व्यक्ति से मिलते हैं जो पेंगुइन से बात कर सकता है, तो आप वास्तव में किसी बहुत खास व्यक्ति से मिलते हैं। उसने एक बड़ा जीवन जिया है और कुछ उल्लेखनीय चीजें की हैं, उनमें से एक है उसका छोटा सा घर बनाना। एक बहुत ही खास घर जो उसकी आत्मा को छूता है।

और यह घर! सुंदर और चरित्र से भरा हुआ। यह पर्याप्त है, और फिर भी यह बहुत कुछ है। सुंदर आकृतियों और सभी अद्भुत अलंकरणों से यह एक ऐसा घर है जो घर की बहुत वास्तविक अनुभूति को विकीर्ण करता है।

प्रकृति में बहुत कम समकोण होते हैं, और यह विशेषता इस छोटे से घर में भी है। फिलिपा और उसके बिल्डरों के लिए प्यार का एक सच्चा श्रम, यह एक छोटा सा घर है जिसे भुलाया नहीं जा सकता। पवित्र ज्यामितीय सिद्धांतों को ध्यान में रखते हुए बनाया गया, यह बहुत आसानी से आपका नया पसंदीदा छोटा घर हो सकता है। हमें बहुत उम्मीद है कि आपको यह टूर पसंद आएगा।

आप फिलिपा, उनके लेखन और उनके पॉडकास्ट को सुनने के लिए लिंक के बारे में उनकी वेबसाइट के माध्यम से अधिक जानकारी प्राप्त कर सकते हैं: https://philippaross.com

यदि आपको हमारा शो पसंद है और आप हमारे काम का समर्थन करना चाहते हैं, तो कृपया पैट्रियन पर हमारा समर्थन करने पर विचार करें: https://www.patreon.com/livingbig

हमारे सोशल और लिंक: https://linktr.ee/livingbig

इस छोटे से घर और अन्य के बारे में हमारी वेबसाइट पर अधिक जानकारी प्राप्त करें: https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/

कृपया छोटे घरों, वास्तुकला, DIY, डिजाइन और संधारणीय, ऑफ-ग्रिड जीवन पर अधिक वीडियो के लिए सदस्यता लें।

fr-FR.title: Une petite maison exquise et insolite construite avec la géométrie de la nature
fr-FR.description:
Cette petite maison a immédiatement conquis mon cœur. Son toit incurvé, ses vitraux et ses portes arrondies évoquent une maison de hobbit moderne, empreint de chaleur, de caractère et de confort.

Philippa est une femme remarquable. J'ai énormément apprécié les moments passés avec elle. Je sais toujours quand je rencontre une âme sœur, et c'est ce que j'ai ressenti avec elle. On sait que rencontrer quelqu'un qui peut parler aux pingouins, c'est rencontrer quelqu'un de vraiment spécial. Elle a eu une vie riche et accompli des choses remarquables. L'une d'elles est la construction de sa petite maison. Une maison sur mesure qui chante à son âme.

Et cette maison ! Magnifique et pleine de caractère. Elle est suffisante, et pourtant, elle est bien plus que cela. De par ses formes élégantes et ses magnifiques décorations, cette maison dégage une véritable sensation de chez-soi.

La nature a très peu d'angles droits, et cette petite maison partage cette caractéristique. Fruit d'un véritable travail d'amour de Philippa et de ses constructeurs, cette petite maison est inoubliable. Conçue selon les principes de la géométrie sacrée, cette mini-maison pourrait bien devenir votre nouvelle préférée. Nous espérons que vous apprécierez la visite.

Pour en savoir plus sur Philippa, ses écrits et écouter son podcast, rendez-vous sur son site web : https://philippaross.com

Si vous appréciez notre émission et souhaitez nous soutenir, n'hésitez pas à nous soutenir sur Patreon : https://www.patreon.com/livingbig

Nos réseaux sociaux et liens : https://linktr.ee/livingbig

Pour en savoir plus sur cette mini-maison et d'autres, consultez notre site web : https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/

Abonnez-vous pour découvrir plus de vidéos sur les mini-maisons, l'architecture, le bricolage, le design et la vie durable et autonome.

Présenté et produit par : Bryce Langston
Caméra : Rasa Pescud et Bryce Langston
Montage : Sarah Binder et Rasa Pescud

Musique du titre de cette vidéo : Bryce Langston : http://www.youtube.com/brycelangston

snippet.title: Buying an Abandoned Shark and Transforming Its Home!
snippet.description:
🌎Get an exclusive 15% discount on Saily data plans! Use code THEFISHGUYS at checkout. Download Saily app or go to https://saily.com/thefishguys ⛵

I just found the craziest deal on Facebook Marketplace—a completely abandoned marbled cat shark setup. The tank was a wreck, but I saw the potential, and you KNOW I had to take on the challenge! 💪In this video, we completely transform this neglected tank into the ultimate shark paradise. We’re talking a custom cave, an underground tunnel, and even a feeding dock at the surface so we can hand-feed the shark like a total beast! 🦈🔥 From the sketchy pickup to the insane final reveal, this was one of the most intense projects I’ve ever done. Did the shark love his new home? You’ll have to watch and find out! 👀

snippet.title: Kevin Hart Celebrates 10 Years of Hot Ones While Eating Spicy Wings | Hot Ones
snippet.description:
On March 12, 2015, Hot Ones premiered to the world with Sean Evans serving up hot questions and even hotter wings for Tony Yayo. Now, we celebrate the show's 10th anniversary with one of the giants of Hot Ones history, Kevin Hart. He's an actor, producer, director, and entrepreneuer—not to mention one of the most successful stand-up comedians of all time. Check out the animated series based on his childhood, Lil Kev, now streaming on BET+, as well as his tequila Gran Coramino, and a new two-part documentary film called Number One on the Call Sheet, which premieres on Apple TV March 28th. But how is he with spicy food? Find out as the man who proclaimed "what y'all got going on here is genius!" when he first appeared on the show takes on the wings of death and discusses his beloved Philadelphia Eagles, action-movie stunts gone wrong, and the impact of Hot Ones on media. Thanks for rocking with us for a decade, Spice Lords!

snippet.title: Rainbow Six Siege X Reveal Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The biggest evolution Rainbow Six Siege has ever seen! Watch livestreams to get BETA access, from March 13 to 19.

In June 2025, the game enters a new era with Siege X, the biggest and most transformative evolution in its history. This milestone will bring a visual overhaul, an enhanced player experience and gameplay changes that deepen the game’s tactical core.

Learn more: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Music by Ark of Noah, Y2 performing Walk Through The Fire

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

About Rainbow Six Siege:
Rainbow Six Siege is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6Siege 

About Ubisoft:
Ubisoft is a creator of worlds, committed to enriching players’ lives with original and memorable entertainment experiences. Ubisoft’s global teams create and develop a deep and diverse portfolio of games, featuring brands such as Assassin’s Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids®, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®, The Crew® and Tom Clancy’s The Division®. Through Ubisoft Connect, players can enjoy an ecosystem of services to enhance their gaming experience, get rewards and connect with friends across platforms. With Ubisoft+, the subscription service, they can access a growing catalog of more than 100 Ubisoft games and DLC. For the 2023-24 fiscal year, Ubisoft generated net bookings of €2.32 billion. To learn more, please visit: www.ubisoftgroup.com.

© 2024 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. Ubisoft and the Ubisoft logo are registered trademarks in the US and/or other countries.

pl.title: Rainbow Six Siege X - zwiastun rozgrywki
pl.description:
Największa ewolucja, jaką kiedykolwiek widziało Rainbow Six Siege! Oglądaj transmisje na żywo od 13 do 19 marca, aby uzyskać dostęp do wersji BETA.

W czerwcu 2025 roku gra wkracza w nową epokę dzięki Siege X, największej i najbardziej widowiskowej ewolucji w historii serii. Ten milowy krok przyniesie zmiany w warstwie wizualnej, a także poprawione wrażenia oraz zmiany w rozgrywce, które jeszcze bardziej zwiększą głębię taktyczną gry.

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

Rainbow Six Siege to ekscytujące, nowe podejście do strzelanek FPS, które w centrum akcji stawia taktyczną walkę i mistrzowską destrukcję. Poprowadź swój zespół wyjątkowych operatorów przez napięte i ekscytujące scenariusze walki i osiągnij zwycięstwo dzięki inteligentnemu przygotowaniu i strategicznej improwizacji. ko.title: 'Rainbow Six Siege X 공개 게임 플레이 트레일러
ko.description:
Rainbow Six Siege 사상 최대의 진화! 3월 14일부터 20일까지 라이브스트리밍을 시청하고 베타 참가 권한을 얻으십시오.

2025년 7월, Siege X가 새로운 시대를 엽니다. Siege 사상 최고로 거대하고 변혁적인 진화를 맞이하십시오. 그래픽 개선, 향상된 플레이어 경험, 게임의 전술적 핵심에 깊이를 더하는 게임 플레이 변경이 담긴 이정표를 직접 경험하십시오.

fr.title: Rainbow Six Siege X - Trailer de présentation du gameplay
fr.description:
L'évolution la plus importante de l'histoire de Rainbow Six Siege ! Regardez les diffusions en direct pour accéder à la BÊTA, du 13 au 19 mars.

En juin 2025, le jeu entrera dans une nouvelle ère avec Siege X, l'évolution la plus importante et novatrice de son histoire. Cette étape apporte une refonte visuelle, une expérience de jeu améliorée et des changements de gameplay qui approfondissent les fondations tactiques du jeu.

« Walk Through The Fire », composée et interprétée par Ark of Noah et Y2

Rainbow Six Siege est une nouvelle approche passionnante du jeu de tir à la première personne (FPS). Les confrontations en combats rapprochés, les tactiques, le travail d'équipe et les actions explosives sont au cœur de l'expérience. Dirigez votre équipe d'agents uniques dans des scénarios de combat intenses et remportez la victoire grâce à des stratégies poussées, baignant dans l'héritage des précédents jeux Rainbow Six.
Rainbow Six Siege est disponible dès maintenant sur Xbox, PlayStation® et PC.

#Ubisoft #R6Siege

Ubisoft est un créateur de mondes qui s’engage à enrichir la vie des joueurs à travers des expériences de jeu uniques et mémorables. Ses équipes internationales créent et développent un portefeuille varié de jeux, comprenant des marques telles qu’Assassin’s Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, The Lapins CrétinsTM, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®, The Crew® et Tom Clancy’s The Division®. Grâce à Ubisoft Connect, les joueurs profitent d’un écosystème de services pour aller plus loin dans leur expérience de jeu, obtenir des récompenses et rester en contact avec leurs amis quelle que soit leur plateforme. 「シージ」が、いまだかつてないほどの進化を遂げる！Live配信で3月14日午前2時（日本時間）から20日午前4時（日本時間）の間に解放されるベータ版へのアクセス情報をチェック！

#Ubisoft #彩虹六号围攻

关于育碧：
育碧（Ubisoft）致力于通过创建世界，为玩家带来新颖深刻的娱乐体验。育碧全球团队打造了丰富多元的游戏作品，拥有《刺客信条》、《英灵乱战》、《荣耀战魂》、《孤岛惊魂》、《舞力全开》、《疯狂兔子》、《飙酷车神》、《彩虹六号》、《全境封锁》等畅销游戏品牌。育碧通过Ubisoft Connect为玩家提供周到全面的服务、游戏内奖励，以及跨平台社交功能，进一步提升游玩体验。育碧在2023-2024财年内实现了23.2亿欧元的净销售收入。

自1996 年在中国建立工作室以来，育碧一直站在中国游戏产业的前沿。目前，育碧中国在上海和成都拥有两处工作室，1000多名来自国内外游戏制作、图像设计、动画、程序、人工智能、音效、测试及数据管理方面的专业人才。

©2024年 育碧娱乐有限公司。育碧保留一切权利。育碧和育碧相关标识均为美国或其他国家注册商标。

es.title: Tráiler de presentación de Rainbow Six Siege X: Mecánicas del juego
es.description:
¡La mayor evolución jamás vista en Rainbow Six Siege! Sigue las retransmisiones para conseguir acceso a la BETA del 13 al 19 de marzo.

En junio de 2025, el juego entra en una nueva era con Siege X, la evolución más grande y transformadora de su historia. Este hito trae consigo una renovación visual, una experiencia de juego mejorada y cambios en la jugabilidad que profundizan en la esencia táctica del juego.

Más información: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Música de Ark of Noah, con Y2 interpretando Walk Through The Fire

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

Sobre Rainbow Six Siege:
Rainbow Six Siege es un shooter táctico, realista, de élite por equipos donde una planificación y una ejecución superiores llevan a la victoria. Su jugabilidad ofrece enfrentamientos de 5 contra 5 de ataque y defensa e intensos combates de rango cercano en entornos destructibles.
Rainbow Six Siege está disponible para PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, la familia de consolas de Xbox One, Xbox Series X | S, Windows PC (incluyendo Ubisoft+, el servicio de suscripción de Ubisoft*) y Amazon Luna. El juego está optimizado para PlayStation®5 y Xbox Series X (con soporte hasta 4K y 120 FPS).

#Ubisoft #R6Siege

Sobre Ubisoft:
Ubisoft es un creador de mundos, comprometido con enriquecer las vidas de los jugadores a través de experiencias de entretenimiento originales e inolvidables. Los equipos globales de Ubisoft crean y desarrollan un catálogo de juegos amplio y variado que incluye marcas como Assassin’s Creed ®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids®, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®, The Crew® y Tom Clancy’s The Division®. Gracias a Ubisoft Connect los jugadores pueden disfrutar de un ecosistema de servicios creados para mejorar su experiencia de juego, conseguir recompensas y conectar con sus amigos en todas las plataformas. Con Ubisoft+, el servicio de suscripción, pueden acceder a un creciente catálogo de más de 100 juegos y DLCs. En el año fiscal 2023-24, Ubisoft registró unos ingresos netos de 2320 millones de euros. Para obtener más información, visita: www.ubisoftgroup.com.  

© 2024 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. Ubisoft and the Ubisoft logo are registered trademarks in the US and/or other countries.

it.title: Trailer di presentazione gameplay Rainbow Six Siege X
it.description:
L'evoluzione più grande mai vista su Rainbow Six Siege! Guarda le dirette per ottenere l'accesso alla BETA, dal 13 al 19 marzo.

A giugno 2025, il gioco entra in una nuova era con Siege X, l'evoluzione più grande e trasformativa nella sua storia. Questo traguardo porterà con sé un aggiornamento grafico, un'esperienza giocatore migliorata e modifiche di gameplay che rendono più profonda la tattica del gioco.

Scopri di più: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Musica di Ark of Noah, Y2 esegue Walk Through The Fire

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

Informazioni su  Rainbow Six Siege:
Rainbow Six Siege è un nuovo, eccitante approccio all'esperienza degli sparatutto in prima persona che mette combattimento tattico e demolizioni da manuale al centro dell'azione. Comanda la tua squadra di Operatori unici attraverso scenari elettrizzanti pieni di tensione e arriva alla vittoria pianificando con astuzia e strategia. Rainbow Six Siege è disponibile su Xbox, PlayStation® e PC.

#Ubisoft #R6Siege

Informazioni su Ubisoft: 
Ubisoft è creatore di mondi, si dedica ad arricchire la vita dei giocatori con esperienze di gioco originali e memorabili. I suoi team in tutto il mondo creano e sviluppano un diversificato portfolio di giochi che comprendono marchi come Assassin’s Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®, The Crew® e Tom Clancy’s The Division®. Tramite Ubisoft Connect, i giocatori possono sperimentare un ecosistema di servizi per migliorare la propria esperienza di gioco, ottenere ricompense e connettersi con amici attraverso differenti piattaforme. Con Ubisoft+, il servizio di abbonamento di Ubisoft, possono accedere a un crescente catalogo di più di 100 giochi Ubisoft e DLC. Per l’anno fiscale 2023-24 Ubisoft ha realizzato un fatturato di 2.320 milioni di euro. Per maggiori informazioni consulta il sito: www.ubisoftgroup.com.  

© 2024 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. Ubisoft and the Ubisoft logo are registered trademarks in the US and/or other countries.

zh-Hant.title: 《虹彩六號：圍攻行動 X》揭露實機預告片
zh-Hant.description:
《圍攻行動》史上最高革新！觀看直播，取得在 3 月 14 日至 20 日期間參與 BETA 測試的資格。

《圍攻行動》將隨著《虹彩六號：圍攻行動 X》在 2025 年 6 月邁入新時代，這是《虹彩六號》史上最重大的革新。這項里程碑將帶來視覺的完整重製、強化過的玩家體驗和遊戲變更，進一步提升遊戲戰術核心的層次。

了解詳情：https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Ark of Noah、Y2 -〈Walk Through The Fire〉

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

關於《虹彩六號：圍攻行動》
《虹彩六號：圍攻行動》帶來了精彩刺激、全新取向的第一人稱射擊遊戲體驗，著重戰術戰鬥和精心策劃的破壞行動。你將帶領由獨特幹員組成的隊伍面對緊張萬分、驚心動魄的戰鬥場面，並透過充分準備和隨機應變取得勝利。《虹彩六號：圍攻行動》已在 Xbox、PlayStation® 和 PC 平台上推出。

#Ubisoft #虹彩六號圍攻行動

關於 Ubisoft：
Ubisoft 是開發、發行與經銷互動式娛樂遊戲與服務的領導廠商，旗下擁有豐富多元的全球知名品牌，包括《刺客教條》、《英靈神殿大亂鬥》、《極地戰嚎》、《榮耀戰魂》、《Just Dance 舞力全開》、《看門狗》、《瘋狂兔子》，以及包含《火線獵殺》、《虹彩六號》和《全境封鎖》的《湯姆克蘭西》電玩遊戲系列。透過 Ubisoft Connect，玩家可享用豐富且完整的服務以提升遊戲體驗、獲得獎勵和與不同平台上的好友互動。訂閱 Ubisoft+ 服務，玩家甚至可以暢玩超過 100 款 Ubisoft 遊戲及擴充內容。Ubisoft 遍及全球各地的開發工作室與辦事處團隊致力於在包含家用遊樂器主機、行動裝置、平板電腦和 PC 等所有熱門遊戲平台上，提供玩家富有原創性且令人回味無窮的遊戲體驗。2023-24 會計年度 Ubisoft 的預定淨收入為 23 億 2 千萬歐元。如欲取得更進一步資訊，請造訪 www.ubisoftgroup.com/。

© 2024 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. Ubisoft and the Ubisoft logo are registered trademarks in the US and/or other countries.

th.title: Rainbow Six Siege X เผยตัวอย่างเกมเพลย์
th.description:
วิวัฒนาการครั้งยิ่งใหญ่ที่สุดที่ Rainbow Six Siege เท่าที่เคยมีมา! รับชมไลฟ์สตรีมตั้งแต่วันที่ 13 ถึง 19 มีนาคม เพื่อรับสิทธิ์เข้าใช้งานในระบบเบต้า

ในเดือนมิถุนายน 2568 เกมนี้จะเข้าสู่ยุคใหม่ Siege X ซึ่งเป็นวิวัฒนาการที่ยิ่งใหญ่ที่สุดและสร้างการเปลี่ยนแปลงมากที่สุดในประวัติศาสตร์ เหตุการณ์สำคัญครั้งนี้จะมาพร้อมกับการปรับปรุงภาพใหม่ ประสบการณ์การเล่นที่ดียิ่งขึ้น และการเปลี่ยนแปลงรูปแบบการเล่นที่ทำให้แก่นหลักของเกมในการเล่นแบบยุทธวิธีมีความเข้มข้นมากยิ่งขึ้น

เรียนรู้เพิ่มเติม: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

ดนตรีโดย Ark of Noah และ Y2 ร่วมกันแสดง Walk Through The Fire

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

เกี่ยวกับเรนโบว์ ซิกซ์ ซีจ:
เรนโบว์ ซิกซ์ ซีจ คือประสบการณ์แห่งเกมยิงมุมมองบุคคลที่หนึ่งแนวใหม่ที่จะนำเอาการต่อสู้เชิงกลยุทธ์และระบบการทำลายล้างอันยอดเยี่ยมมาเป็นศูนย์กลางของแอ็กชันทุกอย่าง นำทีมเจ้าหน้าที่อันเปี่ยมไปด้วยเอกลักษณ์ของคุณผ่านการต่อสู้อันตึงเครียดสุดระทึก แล้วคว้าชัยชนะด้วยการเตรียมตัวอันชาญฉลาดและการปรับตัวด้านกลยุทธ์ เรนโบว์ ซิกซ์ ซีจพร้อมให้เล่นแล้วบน Xbox, PlayStation® และ PC

#Ubisoft #R6Siege

เกี่ยวกับ Ubisoft
Ubisoft คือผู้สร้างสรรค์, มุ่งมั่นที่จะเติมเต็มชีวิตของผู้เล่นด้วยประสบการณ์ความบันเทิงที่เป็นต้นฉบับและน่าจดจำ ทีมงานระดับโลกของ Ubisoft ได้สร้างและพัฒนาผลงานเกมที่ลึกซึ้งและหลากหลาย โดยมีแบรนด์ต่าง ๆ อาทิ Assassin's Creed ®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy's Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids, Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six®, The Crew® และ Tom Clancy's The Division® ผู้เล่นสามารถเพลิดเพลินกับระบบนิเวศการบริการที่รองรับตัวเกม เพื่อยกระดับประสบการณ์การเล่น รับรางวัล และเชื่อมต่อกับเพื่อนฝูง ผ่านแพลตฟอร์ม Ubisoft Connect ด้วยบริการสมัครสมาชิก Ubisoft+ พวกเขาสามารถเข้าถึงแคตตาล็อกเกมและ DLC ของ Ubisoft ที่ยังคงเพิ่มขึ้นอย่างต่อเนื่องมากกว่า 100 เกม สำหรับปีงบประมาณ 2566-2567 Ubisoft มีรายได้ทางบัญชีสุทธิที่ 2,320 ล้านยูโร หากต้องการเรียนรู้เพิ่มเติม โปรดไปที่: www.ubisoftgroup.com

pt-BR.title: Revelação de Rainbow Six Siege X — Trailer do jogo
pt-BR.description:
A maior evolução que Rainbow Six Siege já viu! Assista às transmissões ao vivo para acessar o beta, de 13 a 19 de março.

Em junho de 2025, o jogo entra em uma nova era com Siege X, a maior e a mais transformadora evolução de sua história. Esse marco proporcionará uma reformulação visual, uma experiência aprimorada para os jogadores e mudanças na jogabilidade que aprofundam os princípios táticos do jogo.

Saiba mais: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Música de Ark of Noah, com Y2 interpretando Walk Through The Fire

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

Sobre Rainbow Six Siege:
Rainbow Six Siege é uma nova e  empolgante experiência de jogos de tiro em primeira pessoa. Confrontos de combate corpo a corpo, tático, trabalho em equipe e ações explosivas estão no centro da experiência. Lidere sua equipe de agentes únicos em um cenários de combate intenso e alcance a vitória por meio de estratégias avançadas, baseadas no legado dos jogos anteriores do Rainbow Six.
Rainbow Six Siege já está disponível para Xbox, PlayStation® e PC.

snippet.description:

Lyrics:

Wasting time driving through the Eastside
Doing my thing cause I can’t decide if we’re through
Well are we? 
And if we are 
What we gonna do?

Relationships
What’s all this talk about relationships?
It feels like everyone's caught up in it
Oh just you wait you must be new to this

You got a look on your face like you’re caught in a lie
I got you all to myself but I keep asking why 
In this relationship

Baby how can I explain 
When an innocent mistake
Turns into seventeen days
Fucking relationships
Don’t they end up all the same
When there’s no one left to blame?
I think I’m in love but I can’t stand
Fucking relationships

Why do I have a guilty conscience?
I've always been averse to conflict
But you really fucked with my confidence

You gotta tell me the truth if you don’t want to try
I hear a voice in my head and it keeps asking
Why am I in this relationship?

Baby how can I explain 
When an innocent mistake
Turns into seventeen days
Fucking relationships
Don’t they end up all the same
When there’s no one left to blame?
I think I’m in love but I can’t stand
Fucking relationships

How did we get ourselves into this?
Oh this can’t just be the way it is
Or is it just the shit our parents did
And had to live with it
In their relationship?
Fucking relationships

Baby how can I explain 
When an innocent mistake
Turns into seventeen days
Fucking relationships
Don’t they end up all the same
When there’s no one left to blame?
I think I’m in love but I can’t stand
Communicating it

Let me tell you how it ends
When we can’t even pretend
Feels like we’re not even friends
In this relationship

But I would do it all again
If you put down your defenses 
I think I’m in love so why am I trying to 
Escape from it?

Maybe that’s just how it goes
When you’re not fully grown
But baby when you know you know
Fucking relationships
So don’t let it bring you down 
Cause it all comes back around

I think I’m in love but I can’t stand 
Fucking relationships

snippet.title: América vs Guadalajara | 2025 Concacaf Champions Cup | Round of 16
snippet.description:
Resumen del Partido 🎥

América 🆚 Guadalajara

#ConcaChampions #concacaf #championscap #america #guadalajara #highlights

Club América won 4-nil against CD Guadalajara in the second leg of their Round of 16 series, winning 4-1 on aggregate, on Wednesday in the 2025 Concacaf Champions Cup at Estadio Ciudad de los Deportes in Mexico City, Mexico.

Chivas won 1-nil at home in the opening encounter in Guadalajara, Mexico last Wednesday. The match was the third meeting in a week between the Mexican rivals, with the two meeting in league play on Saturday.

Brian Rodríguez scored in the 6' with a left-footed hit into the right-side netting, equalizing on aggregate.

Diego Valdés got on the board for Las Águilas in the 45', slotting home a loose ball in the box. Rodríguez created the chance with a cross into the box that was punched away by Guadalajara goalkeeper Raúl Rangel.

Alan Mozo was sent off in the 46’ after receiving a double yellow card, leaving CD Guadalajara with ten men.

Alejandro Zendejas extended the lead for the Mexico City side in the 65', striking at the right post on a whipped-in ball from Rodríguez. 

Álvaro Fidalgo added a fourth in the 79’, striking inside the penalty arc to place the exclamation point on the Clásico de México victory.

The series win sets up another rivalry encounter for Club América, who will face fellow Mexico City club Cruz Azul in the quarterfinals.

snippet.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2025 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
snippet.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2025

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 8th of March Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2025 Charity Match at Wembley Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:10pm GMT

Kick off time is at 3pm GMT

The Sidemen Charity Match 2025 is in aid of the following charities and funds raised will be split as follows:

Bright Side 43%
BBC Children in Need 50%
M7 Education 7%

We will also donate all of the profit we make through the match and related activities to the following charities:

Bright Side 86%
M7 Education 14%

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! We hope you enjoy the match.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit https://sidemenfc.com.

Viewers of this livestream are strictly prohibited from re-streaming or rebroadcasting this content on any platform. Any unauthorised re-streaming will result in the immediate removal of the infringing livestream and a copyright strike issued to the violator.

snippet.title: Hammond & May FINALLY Return to Top Gear HQ
snippet.description:
For reasons that are still unclear, Richard Hammond and I decided to revisit the old Top Gear office—the place where we spent an alarming number of years faffing about in the name of car-based television. It’s been nearly a decade since we were last here, although now it feels like yesterday.

Try my gin: https://jamesmaysgin.com/TopGear

Check out my merch: https://jamesmaysgin.com/Merch
Follow me on Insta: https://www.instagram.com/jamesmaygin/

Keep an eye on @Drivetribe for more videos of Hammond and May at Dunsfold 👀

snippet.title: Team TaylorMade SWAPS Drivers For A Straightest Drive Contest...
snippet.description:
Team TaylorMade is back together and in this video, they're going to be switching Qi35 Drivers and competing in a straightest drive competition. 

Each person will walk around the bags while music plays and when the music stops, they have to hit whoever's driver they land on. The two golfers who hit it most off-line will be eliminated, and the last golfer standing wins. 

This all shows why it's so important to get fit for a Qi35 Driver that is optimized for YOUR game. 

Tiger Woods is MC, and Scottie Scheffler, Nelly Korda, Rory McIlroy, Collin Morikawa, Tommy Fleetwood, Charley Hull, and Brooke Henderson are playing. Watch till the end for a special surprise from Tiger. 

Learn more about TaylorMade fittings here: https://tmgolf.co/YTQi35Fittings 

Follow TaylorMade Golf on social media: https://www.instagram.com/taylormadegolf/ https://twitter.com/TaylorMadeGolf https://www.tiktok.com/@taylormadegolf

zh-Hant.title: 《流亡黯道2》：內容更新 0.2.0 預告片
zh-Hant.description:
兩個禮拜後，準時收看 twitch.tv/pathofexile，獲得《流亡黯道2》下一個內容更新的所有資訊！

 在實況期間，玩家將能得知《流亡黯道2》0.2.0 內容更新的所有情報。 實況結束後，Jonathan 與 Mark 會在直播中的問與答環節，與 ZiggyD 一起回答玩家迫切想知道的問題，並在隨後附上完整的 0.2.0 更新檔說明。

 從 4 月 5 日開始，玩家就可以在 PC 和主機上玩到 0.2.0 內容更新。 我們等不及想讓各位看看我們的成果了！

fr.title: Path of Exile 2 : teaser de la mise à jour de contenu 0.2.0
fr.description:
Dans deux semaines, rendez-vous sur twitch.tv/pathofexile afin de tout savoir à propos de notre nouvelle mise à jour de contenu pour Path of Exile 2 ! 

Pendant le stream d'annonce en direct, vous découvrirez tout ce qu'il y a à savoir à propos de la mise à jour 0.2.0 de Path of Exile 2. Après le stream d'annonce, Jonathan et Mark répondront à vos questions les plus pressantes dans le cadre d'une session de Q&R en compagnie de ZiggyD, suivie des patch notes complètes de la 0.2.0.

Vous pourrez jouer à la version 0.2.0 à partir du 4 avril (CEST) sur PC et consoles. Nous sommes impatients de vous dévoiler tout ce sur quoi nous avons travaillé !

ko.title: 패스 오브 엑자일 2: 0.2.0 콘텐츠 업데이트 티저
ko.description:
2주 후, twitch.tv/pathofexile에서 패스 오브 엑자일 2의 다음 콘텐츠 업데이트에 대한 모든 정보를 공개합니다!

이번 라이브스트림에서는 패스 오브 엑자일 2의 0.2.0 콘텐츠 업데이트에 대한 상세 내용을 확인할 수 있습니다. 방송이 끝난 후에는 Jonathan과 Mark가 ZiggyD와 함께 실시간 Q&A 세션을 진행하며, 이후 0.2.0 패치노트 전체 내용도 공개할 예정입니다.

0.2.0 콘텐츠 업데이트는 4월 5일 (한국 시각) PC 및 콘솔에서 플레이할 수 있습니다. 

새로운 콘텐츠를 여러분께 선보일 생각에 무척 기대됩니다!

de.title: Path of Exile 2: Teaser zum Content-Update 0.2.0
de.description:
Seid in zwei Wochen live auf twitch.tv/pathofexile dabei, um alles Wichtige über unser nächstes Content-Update für Path of Exile 2 zu erfahren!

Während des Livestreams erfahrt ihr alles zum Content-Update 0.2.0 für Path of Exile 2. Nach dem Livestream werden Jonathan und Mark in einer Live-Fragerunde mit ZiggyD eure brennenden Fragen beantworten, wonach wir die vollständigen Patch-Notes für 0.2.0 veröffentlichen werden.

Am 4. April erscheint das Content-Update 0.2.0 für PC und Konsolen. Wir freuen uns darauf, euch zu zeigen, woran wir gearbeitet haben!

en-GB.title: Path of Exile 2: Content Update 0.2.0 Teaser
en-GB.description:
In two weeks tune in to twitch.tv/pathofexile to get all the information about our next content update for Path of Exile 2! 

During the livestream you'll learn all about the 0.2.0 content update for Path of Exile 2. After the livestream, Jonathan and Mark will answer your burning questions live in a Q&A session with ZiggyD, which we will follow up with the full 0.2.0 patch notes.

You'll be able to play the 0.2.0 content update on PC and Consoles on April 4th (PDT). We are very excited to show you what we've been working on!

th.title: Path of Exile 2: ทีเซอร์แพทช์อัพเดทเนื้อหา 0.2.0
th.description:
ติดตามชมข้อมูลแพทช์ใหม่สำหรับ Path of Exile 2 กันได้ที่ twitch.tv/pathofexile ในสองสัปดาห์ข้างหน้านี้!

ในการถ่ายทอดสดนี้ คุณจะได้รู้ข้อมูลต่างๆ เกี่ยวกับแพทช์อัพเดทเนื้อหา 0.2.0 สำหรับ Path of Exile 2 และเมื่อการถ่ายทอดสดจบลง โจนาธานกับมาร์คจะมาร่วมกับ ZiggyD เพื่อตอบคำถามคาใจของคุณกันสดๆ ในช่วงตอบคำถามค่ะ และเราจะปิดท้ายด้วยการอัพรายละเอียดแพทช์ตัวเต็มให้อ่านกัน

คุณจะได้เล่นแพทช์อัพเดทเนื้อหา 0.2.0 ในระบบ PC และคอนโซลในวันที่ 5 เมษายนนี้ (เวลาไทย) เราตั้งตารอนำเสนอผลงานของเราอยู่นะคะ!

en.title: Path of Exile 2: Dawn of the Hunt Teaser
en.description:
In two weeks tune in to twitch.tv/pathofexile to get all the information about our next content update for Path of Exile 2! 

During the livestream you'll learn all about the 0.2.0 content update for Path of Exile 2. After the livestream, Jonathan and Mark will answer your burning questions live in a Q&A session with ZiggyD, which we will follow up with the full 0.2.0 patch notes.

You'll be able to play the 0.2.0 content update on PC and Consoles on April 4th (PDT). We are very excited to show you what we've been working on!

ru.title: Path of Exile 2: Тизер контентного обновления 0.2.0
ru.description:
Через две недели подключайтесь к twitch.tv/pathofexile, чтобы узнать всё о следующем контентном обновлении для Path of Exile 2!

Во время прямой трансляции вы узнаете все подробности о контентном обновлении 0.2.0 для Path of Exile 2. После стрима Джонатан и Марк ответят на самые горячие вопросы в прямом эфире во время Q&A-сессии с ZiggyD. Затем мы опубликуем полный список изменений версии 0.2.0.

Дополнение 0.2.0 будет доступно для игры на ПК и консолях 4 апреля (PDT). Мы с нетерпением ждём момента, когда сможем показать вам, над чем работали!

es.title: Adelanto de la actualización 0.2.0 de Path of Exile 2
es.description:
¡En dos semanas, ven a twitch.tv/pathofexile para obtener toda la información sobre nuestra próxima actualización de contenido para Path of Exile 2! 

Durante la transmisión en vivo, descubrirás todo sobre la actualización de contenido 0.2.0 de Path of Exile 2. Después de la transmisión, Jonathan y Mark responderán todas tus preguntas en una sesión de Q&A con ZiggyD, al final de la cual publicaremos las notas completas del parche 0.2.0.

Podrás jugar la actualización de contenido 0.2.0 en PC y consolas el 4 de abril PDT. ¡Estamos muy ansiosos por mostrarte todo en lo que hemos estado trabajando!

pt-BR.title: Path of Exile 2: Teaser da Atualização de Conteúdo 0.2.0
pt-BR.description:
Em duas semanas, fique ligado em twitch.tv/pathofexile para ver todas as informações sobre a nossa próxima atualização e conteúdo para o Path of Exile2!

Durante a transmissão, você terá mais informações sobre a atualização de conteúdo 0.2.0 para o Path of Exile. Após a transmissão, Jonathan e Mark responderão suas perguntas mais frequentes em uma sessão de Q&A com ZiggyD, com as notas do patch saindo logo em seguida.

Você poderá jogar a atualização de conteúdo 0.2.0 gratuitamente no PC e nos Consoles no dia 4 de Abril. Estamos muito empolgados para mostrar no que temos trabalhado!

ja.title: Path of Exile 2:コンテンツアップデートティーザー
ja.description:
2週間後、twitch.tv/pathofexile にて、Path of Exile 2の次回コンテンツアップデートに関する最新情報をお届けします！

ライブ配信では、Path of Exile 2の0.2.0 コンテンツアップデートに関する詳細を紹介します。ライブ配信の後、JonathanとMarkがZiggyDと共に皆さんの疑問にお答えします。そして、配信の後には0.2.0のパッチノート全文も公開予定です。

0.2.0 コンテンツアップデートは4月5日 (日本時間)にPCおよびコンソールでプレイ可能になります。私たちが取り組んできたアップデートをお見せするのが待ちきれません！

snippet.title: Baylee Littrell Auditions With Original Song & Duets with Backstreet Boy Dad Brian! | American Idol
snippet.description:
21 year-old Baylee Littrell is the son of Backsteet Boys' Brian Littrell. Baylee is coming to American Idol to start his own journey of becoming a worldwide-known singer-songwriter. Baylee sings a song he wrote called "Waiting On Myself To Die" and gets high praise from Carrie Underwood, Luke Bryan, and Lionel Richie. Then an unexpected duet happens between Baylee and his Dad Brian! Backstreet's Back, ALRIGHT...and gets a golden ticket to Hollywood!

See more of American Idol 2025 on our official site: http://www.americanidol.com

snippet.title: Sir Jim Ratcliffe: Amorim, Ten Hag, Finances & The Glazers | The Overlap With Gary Neville
snippet.description:
Gary Neville is joined by Sir Jim Ratcliffe on The Overlap, brought to you by Sky Bet. They discuss Manchester United’s season so far, new manager Ruben Amorim, the club’s finances, and what’s next for United.

Ratcliffe reflects on his first year at United, including the controversial decision to replace Erik ten Hag with Ruben Amorim, despite an FA Cup triumph. He also tackles the club’s financial struggles, including a bloated wage bill, and the steps being taken to bring United back to the top.

The conversation also lifts the lid on Dan Ashworth’s departure, what really happened behind the scenes, and how it impacted United’s plans heading into a crucial second half of the Premier League season.

Looking ahead, Gary and Sir Jim discuss the future of Old Trafford, the club’s long-term vision, and whether United fans can find reasons for optimism after a below-par campaign.

Don’t miss this one—hit like, share your thoughts in the comments, and subscribe to stay updated with every episode!

01:13 Facing Scrutiny and Criticism
02:17 Understanding Fan Frustration
02:52 Evaluating Team Performance
03:57 Challenges and Progress
05:13 Recruitment and Management Decisions

21:43 Balancing Finances and Team Success

snippet.title: Finding A Player Who Doesn't Exist
snippet.description:
I received a message on discord from someone asking if I could help them find a friend they hadn't spoken with in a while. The task seemed innocent enough at first, but ended up being one of the most mysterious and darkest rabbit holes I've ever investigated. What happened to Alex? This is finding a minecraft player who doesn't exist.

Channel: @xXCraftykinggXx 

➤➤ Twitter: https://twitter.com/WifiesWasTaken
➤➤ Discord: https://discord.gg/zAWUuWb


➤➤Links: I dont think any? but maybe I'm forgetting 


This is a series called Minecraft VVSauce where I explore random features of Minecraft. Not Secret Minecraft things or Minecraft lore (like Game Theory) or Escape Rooms, but a scary arg based series. The footage in this video isn't of a real person, an ARG is a story that's known to be fictional but we all pretend it's real and try to solve the mystery that the owner of this channel created. Such is the life of an ARG hunter. Very scary very creepy. BOO!

snippet.title: Hiking To The CIA’s “Top Secret” Plane Crash in Death Valley
snippet.description:
Check out the best electrolyte mix out there at https://drinklmnt.com/Brent for a FREE 8-count sample pack! I take LMNT everywhere with me, especially on these long hikes.

In this video, I finally attempt a hike to the legendary crashed CIA plane in the middle of Death Valley. 

This plane was part of a top secret program in the 1950s as part of the United State's Cold War efforts. The program was a joint program between the Air Force and the CIA. Unfortunately, on one cold night in January of 1952, one of these planes crashed on a training mission over Death Valley. 

Due to the remote and difficult nature of getting to the airplane, it was left there. Now, 73 years later, I hiked in to see what it was all about!

I hope you enjoy!

You can follow my journey on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

es-US.title: Caminata hacia el lugar de la CIA donde se estrelló el avión “ultrasecreto” en el Valle de la Muerte
es-US.description:
¡Echa un vistazo a la mejor mezcla de electrolitos que existe en https://drinklmnt.com/Brent para obtener un paquete de muestra GRATIS de 8 unidades! Llevo LMNT a todas partes conmigo, especialmente en estas largas caminatas.

En este video, finalmente intento una caminata hasta el legendario avión de la CIA que se estrelló en medio del Valle de la Muerte. 

Este avión era parte de un programa de alto secreto en la década de 1950 como parte de los esfuerzos de la Guerra Fría de los Estados Unidos. El programa era un programa conjunto entre la Fuerza Aérea y la CIA. Desafortunadamente, en una fría noche de enero de 1952, uno de estos aviones se estrelló en una misión de entrenamiento sobre el Valle de la Muerte. 

Debido a la naturaleza remota y difícil de llegar al avión, lo dejaron allí. Ahora, 73 años después, caminé hasta allí para ver de qué se trataba. 

¡Espero que lo disfrutes! 

Puedes seguir mi recorrido en Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

¡GRACIAS!

ja.title: デスバレーの CIA の「極秘」飛行機墜落現場へのハイキング
ja.description:
https://drinklmnt.com/Brent で最高の電解質ミックスをチェックして、8 個入りの無料サンプル パックを手に入れましょう。私はどこへ行くにも LMNT を持っていきます。特に長いハイキングのときは。

このビデオでは、デス バレーの真ん中で墜落した伝説の CIA 飛行機へのハイキングに挑戦します。

この飛行機は、1950 年代に米国の冷戦対策の一環として極秘で実施されたプログラムの一部でした。このプログラムは空軍と CIA の共同プログラムでした。残念ながら、1952 年 1 月のある寒い夜、この飛行機の 1 機がデス バレー上空の訓練ミッション中に墜落しました。

飛行機にたどり着くのが遠くて困難だったため、飛行機はそのまま残されました。73 年経った今、私はハイキングして、一体何だったのか確かめてきました。

お楽しみください。

id.title: Mendaki ke Lokasi Kecelakaan Pesawat “Rahasia” CIA di Death Valley
id.description:
Lihatlah campuran elektrolit terbaik di https://drinklmnt.com/Brent untuk mendapatkan paket sampel 8 hitungan GRATIS! Saya membawa LMNT ke mana-mana, terutama pada pendakian yang panjang ini.

Dalam video ini, saya akhirnya mencoba mendaki ke pesawat CIA legendaris yang jatuh di tengah Death Valley. 

Pesawat ini merupakan bagian dari program rahasia pada tahun 1950-an sebagai bagian dari upaya Perang Dingin Amerika Serikat. Program ini merupakan program gabungan antara Angkatan Udara dan CIA. Sayangnya, pada suatu malam yang dingin di bulan Januari 1952, salah satu pesawat ini jatuh saat menjalankan misi pelatihan di Death Valley. 

Karena jaraknya yang jauh dan sulit untuk mencapai pesawat tersebut, pesawat itu ditinggalkan di sana. Sekarang, 73 tahun kemudian, saya mendaki untuk melihat seperti apa pesawat itu!

Semoga Anda menikmatinya!

de-DE.title: Wanderung zum „streng geheimen“ Flugzeugabsturz der CIA im Death Valley
de-DE.description:
Schauen Sie sich die beste Elektrolytmischung an, die es gibt, unter https://drinklmnt.com/Brent und erhalten Sie ein KOSTENLOSES 8er-Probepaket! Ich nehme LMNT überall mit hin, besonders auf diese langen Wanderungen.

In diesem Video versuche ich endlich eine Wanderung zu dem legendären abgestürzten CIA-Flugzeug mitten im Death Valley.

Dieses Flugzeug war in den 1950er Jahren Teil eines streng geheimen Programms im Rahmen der Bemühungen der Vereinigten Staaten im Kalten Krieg. Das Programm war ein gemeinsames Programm der Air Force und der CIA. Leider stürzte in einer kalten Nacht im Januar 1952 eines dieser Flugzeuge bei einem Trainingseinsatz über dem Death Valley ab.

Da das Flugzeug so abgelegen und schwer zu erreichen war, wurde es dort zurückgelassen. Jetzt, 73 Jahre später, bin ich dorthin gewandert, um zu sehen, was es damit auf sich hatte!

Ich hoffe, es gefällt Ihnen!

hi.description:

इस वीडियो में, मैं आखिरकार डेथ वैली के बीच में दुर्घटनाग्रस्त हुए CIA के प्रसिद्ध विमान तक पहुँचने का प्रयास करता हूँ।

it.title: Escursione al luogo dell'incidente aereo "top secret" della CIA nella Death Valley
it.description:
Dai un'occhiata al miglior mix di elettroliti in circolazione su https://drinklmnt.com/Brent per un campione GRATUITO da 8 pezzi! Porto LMNT ovunque con me, soprattutto durante queste lunghe escursioni.

In questo video, provo finalmente a fare un'escursione sul leggendario aereo della CIA precipitato nel mezzo della Death Valley.

Questo aereo faceva parte di un programma top secret negli anni '50 come parte degli sforzi degli Stati Uniti durante la Guerra Fredda. Il programma era un programma congiunto tra l'aeronautica militare e la CIA. Sfortunatamente, in una fredda notte di gennaio del 1952, uno di questi aerei si schiantò durante una missione di addestramento sulla Death Valley.

A causa della natura remota e difficile per raggiungere l'aereo, è stato lasciato lì. Ora, 73 anni dopo, ho fatto un'escursione per vedere di cosa si trattava!

fr-FR.title: Randonnée vers le crash de l'avion « top secret » de la CIA dans la Vallée de la Mort
fr-FR.description:
Découvrez le meilleur mélange d'électrolytes disponible sur https://drinklmnt.com/Brent pour un pack d'échantillons GRATUIT de 8 unités ! J'emporte LMNT partout avec moi, surtout lors de ces longues randonnées.

Dans cette vidéo, je tente enfin une randonnée jusqu'au légendaire avion de la CIA écrasé au milieu de la Vallée de la Mort.

Cet avion faisait partie d'un programme top secret dans les années 1950 dans le cadre des efforts de la guerre froide des États-Unis. Le programme était un programme conjoint entre l'armée de l'air et la CIA. Malheureusement, par une nuit froide de janvier 1952, l'un de ces avions s'est écrasé lors d'une mission d'entraînement au-dessus de la Vallée de la Mort.

En raison de la nature éloignée et difficile de l'accès à l'avion, il a été laissé là. Aujourd'hui, 73 ans plus tard, j'ai fait une randonnée pour voir de quoi il s'agissait !

J'espère que vous apprécierez !

snippet.description:
Harvey Specter has officially landed on the West Coast. 

All-new Suits LA - watch NBC on Peacock.

#NBC #SuitsLA

NBC ON SOCIAL:
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/nbc

Facebook: http://Facebook.com/NBC
Instagram: http://instagram.com/nbc

Find NBC trailers, full episode highlights, previews, promos, clips, and digital exclusives here. 

ABOUT SUITS LA:
Ted Black, a former federal prosecutor from New York, has reinvented himself to represent the most powerful clients in Los Angeles. His firm is at a crisis point, and in order to survive, he must embrace a role he held in contempt his entire career. Ted is surrounded by a stellar group of characters who test their loyalties to both Ted and each other while they can’t help but mix their personal and professional lives. All of this is going on while we slowly unravel the events that years ago led Ted to leave behind everything and everyone he loved.

The series stars Stephen Amell, Lex Scott Davis, Josh McDermitt and Bryan Greenberg. Aaron Korsh is writer and executive producer. David Bartis, Doug Liman, Gene Klein, Anton Cropper, Genevieve Sparling, Rick Muirragui and Jon Cowan also executive produce. “Suits LA” is produced by UCP, a division of Universal Studio Group.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: SHOULD YOU TOW WITH A CYBERTRUCK?! - (catastrophic failure test)
snippet.description:
The Tesla Cybertruck is built with a cast aluminum frame. Get up to 40% off your RIDGE wallet here: https://www.ridge.com/JERRYRIG (discount code: JerryRig) Huge thanks to RIDGE for sponsoring my science projects. This helps the cyber truck be manufactured extremely quickly. However - cast aluminum is not good for towing as we see in this Cybertruck durability test video. The hitch breaks around 10,000 pounds. (4500kg) Which is far too close to the 11,000 pound towing capacity. Yikes. 

While the Gigacasting method is *terrible* for the Cybertruck it is actually an amazing manufacturing process for Tesla's other vehicles which i highly recommend: https://ts.la/zack10701

If you want an electric truck that can still tow 11,000lbs and not snap in half - might i recommend a Rivian: https://rivian.com/configurations/list?reprCode=ZACK1594426

snippet.title: Yuval Raphael - New Day Will Rise | Israel 🇮🇱 | Official Music Video | #Eurovision2025
snippet.description:
Subscribe and 🔔 to Eurovision 👉 https://www.youtube.com/user/eurovision?sub_confirmation=1 ​

Yuval Raphael will represent Israel at the Eurovision Song Contest 2025 with the song New Day Will Rise.

~~~ Lyrics ~~~

New Day Will Rise

And even if you say goodbye 
You’ll never go away 
You are the rainbow of my sky 
My colours in the grey
My only wish upon a star 
Sunshine in the day 
The only song that my piano ever plays 

And even if you say goodbye 
You’ll always be around 
To lift me up and take me high 
Keep my feet close to the ground 
Are you proud of me tonight 
Dreams are coming true 
I choose the light 
Nothing to lose if I lose you 

New day will rise
Life will go on 
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But we will stay  
Even if you say goodbye 

‏Et même si tu dis adieu
‏Tu ne partiras jamais
‏T’es l’arc-en-ciel de mon ciel bleu
‏Mes couleurs dans le gris
‏Et mon seul souhait sous un ciel d’art
‏Un rayon dans ma journée
‏La seule chanson que mon piano peut  jouer

New day will rise
Life will go on 
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But we will stay  
Even you say

New day will rise
Life will go on 
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But you will stay  
The love of my life 

מים רבים 
לא יכבו 
את האהבה 
ונהרות לא ישטפוה 

New day will rise
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But we will stay  
Even if you say goodbye 

A new day will rise
New day will rise

snippet.title: We Lived in a Truck Camper for 72 Hours
snippet.description:
A very Aussie 4x4 adventure on Stradbroke "Straddie" Island. Filmed Feb 10-13, 2025. Go to http://DrinkLMNT.com/eamonandbec for a free sample pack with any purchase!

After living in a converted sprinter van for nearly 5 years we thought we'd cracked the code to tiny house on wheels with #vanlife  But, this week we really test ourselves with a brand new setup... a 4X4 truck with a rooftop tent. Not only is it the smallest setup we've ever traveled in but we've also added our 1 year old daughter to the mix. Frankie is such an incredibly adaptable baby but can we really enjoy all that Australia has to offer with a 1 year old child in tow? 

We spot kangaroos, drive a 4X4 rig on some of Australia's most epic beaches and manage to keep up with our mate @MaxandOccy . Make sure you check out his episode for more of our adventures.

snippet.title: We Lived in the NEW $900,000 Earthroamer LTx
snippet.description:
We got to be the first lucky people to take the brand new, one and only EarthRoamer LTx on a roadtrip through the stunning Utah landscapes of Monument Valley and Valley of the Gods! Use our link https://drinkag1.com/karaandnate to subscribe & save $20 off your first subscription!! 
We hope you enjoy this full tour of the new LTx model, plus an epic adventure with some of the best off grid campsites we've ever seen! Plus Nate casually ran a marathon and has a big announcement ;) 

Episode 955 | Filmed February 2025 | Utah

Here are our past EarthRoamer videos :) We're so happy to be friends with this awesome company who lets us go with them on these awesome adventures!! Thanks Zack for another AMAZING trip!  
LTi in Boulder: https://youtu.be/GvvA12oTQ94?si=kauNIgVwO-_6RRum
SX in Moab desert: https://youtu.be/Aw0V9QpcRvc?si=VjJG2n8ccX7fmkD6 
SX in winter Colorado: https://youtu.be/-HUYGx9Qqmg?si=CuaPmj8aY5ujGpVH 

Want to save money on flights and hotels?! Check out our all new  @dailydroppro.travel  😍➡️ 
https://s.dailydrop.com/yt_kn-bfcm24 

——————————————————

✈️  @DailyDrop  is our *FREE travel newsletter!* Get all the best travel news, tips, and tricks every weekday in your inbox by subscribing here ➡️
https://faredrop.app/ytd_220827 

📸 Get behind the scenes content on our Instagram! @karaandnate
https://www.instagram.com/karaandnate/ 

📧 Read our Sunday Summary email to know what goes on between videos -
https://karaandnate.com/sunday-summary/ 

🎶 Here’s where we got all of our copyright free songs used in this episode -
http://bit.ly/epidemic_sound

——————————————————

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s 

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super “normal.” I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of “travel hacking” while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a “one year” trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to “normal life.” We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. 😊🎥🌎 Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

26:39 Valley of the Gods campsite
29:50 first time using invisacook! 
32:32 Nates big announcement! 
34:24 my solo adventure
45:36 smoking dinner
47:42 Final thoughts

snippet.title: Squishy Makeovers  Fixing Your Squishies #38
snippet.description:
Welcome to another episode of squishy makeovers, where I transform ugly, used, old, dirty, cheap or unwanted squishies (donated by my subscribers) into my own creations. I repair, paint and cut away for hours on end to complete these. Hopefully you like them. Get used to lots of rainbow and sprinkles, because I am addicted to both!

Don't forget to check out the CHESS SET!
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

What I'm Using (contains affiliate links):
Squishy Makeovers Fixing Your Squishies #37
Tulip Matte Fabric Paint: https://amzn.to/49OjdMp
Tulip Slick Fabric Paint: https://amzn.to/3LBW6uO
Posca Pens: https://amzn.to/40TgXPL
Scissors: https://amzn.to/3MjSY6L
Sandpaper: https://amzn.to/3EQOOPY
Fabric Hot Glue: https://amzn.to/3PQ4KZh


_______FAQs________

1. CAN I SEND YOU SQUISHIES?
So many generous people have sent me their unwanted squishies so I actually have a lot to work on already, BUT if you desperately want to, you can request my mailing address in the email ALLLL the way at down in the description (sorry for the traveling), make sure to read the disclaimer down there as well.

2. ARE SQUISHIES RETURNED TO THE SENDERS AFTER THE MAKEOVER?
No. These squishies  are sent as donations to the series because they are damaged and/or no longer wanted. Everyone has been informed in advance that squishies would not be returned. 

3. WHAT PAINT DO YOU USE?
I use fabric paint. Fabric paint is meant to stretch, so it is perfect for squishing! Any brand will work fine, but I mainly use Tulip. You can find it at Michaels, Hobby Lobby, A.C. Moore, Walmart, Joann Fabrics, and Online.

5. WILL FABRIC PAINT CRACK?
The matte fabric paint is more likely to crack after lots of squishing. Slick fabric paints never crack. But there are benefits to both. I usually mix the two paints together to get the best of both worlds.

6. CAN I USE ACRYLIC PAINT ON SQUISHIES?
I would not recommend that. Acrylic paint will either make the squishy hard, or it will crack and flake off very easily.


___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Friday at 4:00pm ET

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 29 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chalk full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and various other items I find. I also love to draw, traditionally and digitally. I'm not the most skilled artist out here, but I like to focus on having fun with creativity and being able to laugh at my own mistakes. 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Drawings to Squishies: turning my flat drawings into squishies
Finishing Art Ideas: Choosing art ideas from my giant list and making them happen
Squishies I've Been Avoiding: Painting on the squishies I DON'T want to paint

https://a.co/4XDtrmV

snippet.title: Dolly Parton - If You Hadn’t Been There (Official Audio)
snippet.description:
"If You Hadn’t Been There" by Dolly Parton http://dolly.lnk.to/IYHBT

Lyrics:
(Verse 1)
If you hadn’t been there
Where would I be?
Without your trust
Love and belief
The ups and downs
We’ve always shared
And I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

(Verse 2)
If you hadn’t been you
Well who would I be?
You’ve always seen
The best in me
Your loving arms
Have cradled me
You held me close
And I believe

(1st Chorus)
I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there
Holding my hand
Showing you care
You made me dream
More than I dared
And I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

(Bridge)
Oh you are my rock
A soft Place to land
My wings, my confidence
You understand
Your willingness
Beyond compare
No I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

(2nd Modulated Chorus)
I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there
Pushing me on
When I was scared
I thank God and you
Oh for your loving care
And for giving me love
With more to spare
You made me climb
And top the stairs
I wouldn’t be here
I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there
Oh I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

pl.title: Spędziłem 100 Godzin W Piramidach!
pl.description:
Hej wszystkim! Po raz pierwszy w historii dubbingujemy moje filmy w języku polskim dzięki szalenie ciekawej technologii AI! Nie martw się, to nie tylko sprawa robota - pracowaliśmy z niesamowitym zespołem specjalistów od lokalizacji, aby upewnić się, że wszystko brzmi tak dobrze, jak to tylko możliwe. Ogromne podziękowania za pomoc w realizacji tego projektu należą się również ElevenLabs, polskiej firmie będącej liderem w dziedzinie głosów AI. Jestem bardzo podekscytowany, że mogę się tym z wami podzielić i nie mogę się doczekać, aby usłyszeć, co o tym myślicie. Dajcie znać, czy wam się podoba! ❤️

Nie mogę uwierzyć, że pozwolono nam to zrobić
2 Sezon Swarms jest już dostępny! Możesz nawet znaleźć Złotego Swarms'a o wartości 10 000 $! Kup teraz w Walmart, Target, Amazon lub u najlepszych sprzedawców zabawek na całym świecie. Ten film zawiera treści promowane we współpracy z Moose Toys.

Zobacz dr Zahi Hawassa NA ŻYWO w najbliższym mieście: https://www.hawasszahi.com/2025tour

Nakręcono w Egipcie w piramidach w Gizie, we współpracy z Egipską Komisją Filmową

snippet.title: Beéle - sobelove (Video Oficial)
snippet.description:
Beéle - sobelove (Video Oficial)

Letra
En medio de lo oscuro 
No ha sido fácil y hoy quiero ahogarme 
En los besos tuyos BABY 
YO! yo te lo juro
Somos brillante y como diamante lo nuestro 
Es puro 
Ya dejemo’ el orgullo !

Porque si te toco co co 
Y tú no dices na na na na 
Poco a poco co co co co 
Te voy a enamora ah ah ah ! 

Porque si te toco co co 
Y tú no dices na na na na 
Poco a poco co co co co 
Te voy a enamora ah ah ah ah ah ! 

Tú eres mala, mala, mala, mala tú eres de verdad.
Te tengo amaña y no lo quieres aceptar
Lo que tú quieras jugar conmigo yo quiero jugar 
Y que no y qué tal 
No digas que no 
Aprieta mami que si 
Esta noche un beso te doy 
No te olvidarás de mi 
Y ahí 
Te digo en verdad quien soy 
Lo loco que estoy por ti 
Yo el tiempo que detrás de ti estoy 
Y ahora que vaina mami ! 

Porque si te toco co co 
Y tú no dices na na na na 
Poco a poco co co co co 
Te voy a enamora ah ah ah ! 

Porque si te toco co co 
Y tú no dices na na na na 
Poco a poco co co co co 
Te voy a enamora ah ah ah ah ah !

Sigue a Beéle
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/beele/ 
TikTok https://www.tiktok.com/@beele 
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/beelemusica 

#sobelove #Beéle

snippet.title: Possible Martin Family car pulled from Columbia River in cold case from 1958
snippet.description:
The station wagon presumed to be connected to the Martin Family is set to be pulled out Friday afternoon — more than 65 years after their sudden disappearance in 1958.
